Separation of Concerns 
HTML -> content layer 
CSS -> presentation layer 

HTML -> nouns 
CSS -> adjectives 

HTML -> if webpage is a house htmlis the wooden frames and drywall 
CSS -> paint and wallpaper or roofing and siding 

HTML -> skeleton 
CSS  -> skin, hair, nails, 





